OL,3,CPolice forces see double spike in
OL,4,Creligious hate crimes in past 18 months
OL,6,FSome of the largest police forces in
OL,7,Fthe UK have seen a double spike in
OL,8,Ftypes of religious hate crime in the
OL,9,Fpast 18 months, with numbers jumping
OL,10,Fafter the start of the Hamas-Israel
OL,11,Fconflict in autumn 2023 and again
OL,12,Ffollowing the Southport attacks this
OL,13,Fsummer, figures reveal.
OL,15,FAntisemitic offences recorded by
OL,16,Fforces including Greater Manchester,
OL,17,FWest Midlands and the Metropolitan
OL,18,FPolice, rose sharply in the weeks
OL,19,Ffollowing the outbreak of hostilities
OL,20,Fin the Middle East in October last
OL,21,Fyear.
