OL,6,FThe same forces then logged an
OL,7,Fincrease in Islamophobic offences in
OL,8,Fthe wake of the stabbings in Southport
OL,9,Fin July this year and the subsequent
OL,10,Fviolent disorder in towns and cities.
OL,12,FA Jewish charity called the findings
OL,13,F"unacceptable", while campaigners
OL,14,Fagainst anti-Muslim abuse said they
OL,15,Fwere "not seeing the action to tackle
OL,16,Fthis problem".
OL,18,FThe Government said it was "determined
OL,19,Fto stamp out the toxic vitriol which
OL,20,Fis spread by a minority of people".
