OL,6,FThe figures have been obtained by the
OL,7,FPA news agency using Freedom of
OL,8,FInformation requests. They show that:
OL,10,F` Greater Manchester Police recorded
OL,11,Fan average of 13 antisemitic offences
OL,12,Fper month from January to September
OL,13,F2023, then spikes of 85 in October and
