OL,6,F` The Metropolitan Police changed the
OL,7,Fway it records hate crime at the end
OL,8,Fof February 2024 but, under the
OL,9,Fprevious method, an average of 54
OL,10,Fantisemitic offences were logged per
OL,11,Fmonth in Jan-Sep 2023, followed by a
OL,12,Fsteep rise to 517 in October, 411 in
OL,13,FNovember and 228 in December; while,
OL,14,Funder the new method, an average of
OL,15,F116 Islamophobic offences were
OL,16,Frecorded each month from Mar-Jul 2024,
OL,17,Ffollowed by 190 in August and 97 in
OL,18,FSeptember.
