OL,6,FOther forces covering largely urban
OL,7,Fareas, such as Merseyside, South
OL,8,FYorkshire and West Midlands, saw a
OL,9,Flower volume of these crimes overall
OL,10,Fbut still recorded spikes in
OL,11,Fantisemitic offences in the autumn of
OL,12,F2023 and Islamophobic offences in the
OL,13,Fsummer of 2024.
